version_description:
- Sign up and log in with Apple accounts
- Events tab update and voting service added
- QR/Barcode reader added
- Improved functionality and fixed some minor issues.

1. Chart UI, UX improvements
- Now, you can more conveniently check Hanteo Chart. Check the real-time, daily, weekly, monthly, and yearly Hanteo Chart at a glance.

2. Album authentication function and other bug fixes

1. Whosfan Gold Coin service opens!
- Now, you can participate in the voting with Whosfan Gold Coin. Support your artist with a brand new way! Whosfan Gold Coins can be bought from the Store.
2. Other bug fixes and update
